ing for up to 47 and having a dot that does 1132 damage at my finger tips I wouldnt be complaining about my HT not doing any damage because I know I am dealing a crap load.  You really cant compare HT to LoH if you ask me because think how much LoH must of sucked for Paladins at low lvls compared to your HT.  <br>
